      "text": "brons/ eekſch tahs Semmes Ra-\nnân.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbrââms nahze Sarn\nnoschehloht/ un wiꞥſch aprau-\ndaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pehz zehlahs Ahbrââms/\nno fawa Mixxonu/ un runnaja\nar Etta Behrneem/ fazzidains:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es esmu weens Sweschi-\nneeks/ pee jums/ misdams/ Doh-\ndeet man ihpaschu Kappu/ tad es\naprakſchu fawu Mixxonu/ no\nnannahm Azzim nohſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad atbildeja Etta Behr-\ni Ahbrââmam/ fazzidami uſto:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Klaufi nuhs/ Kungs/ tu\nfi weens Deewiskigs Wirfneeks diu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs Ahbrââms/\nflannijahs preeſsch teem Sem-\nes Landim preeſsch Etta Behr-\netr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch runnaja ar teem/\nzidams: Ja tas junis irr pa\nrahtam/ ka es fawn Mixxonu\nnna Preeſschâ aprohſu/ tad\nufajt mann/ un aisluhdseet\nnnis deht Eewronu Jôira\nehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tas man dohd tawu diw-\nrtiqu Bedri/ kas tam fawa\nbruma Gallâ irr/ tam buhs\nn to par pillu Nandu doht/\nweenu ihpaschu Kappu juhto\nddu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Gewrons mitte ſtarp\nEtta Behrneem: Tad athil-\ndeja Gewrons tas Getiteris Ah-\nbrââmam/ preeſsch Etta Behrnu\nAufim/ un preeſsch wifſeen/ kaſ\nzaur winna Pilsfahta Wahrtim\ngahje/ fazzidains.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne/ mans Kungê/ klaufi\nmann/ to Tihrumu dohnu es\ntew/ un to Bedri/ kas eekſch ta\nirr/ to dohnu es tew/ preeſsch\nmanuo Zaſschu Behrnu Azzim\ndohnu es tew to/ aprohz tawu\nMixxonu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad flannijahs Ahbra-\nams preeſsch teem Semmes Lan-\nteem Semmes Landim dsirdoht/\nfazzidains: Mihrajs/ ja tu grib-\nbi/ klaufi mann luhdsanis: Es\ndohſchu tew to Nandu preeſsch\nta Tihrunna/ nemm to no man-\nnim/ tad aprakſchu es tur fawu\nMixxonu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un runnaja us Gewronu/\nteem Semmes Landim dsirdoht/\nfazzidains: Mihrajs/ ja tu grib-\nbi/ klaufi mann luhdsanis: Es\ndohſchu tew to Nandu preeſsch\nta Tihrunna/ nemm to no man-\nnim/ tad aprakſchu es tur fawu\nMixxonu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Gewrons atbildeja Ah-\nbrââmam/ fazzidams us to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Maus Kungê/ klaufi\nmann/ ta Semme makfa tschetr-\nsints Sudraba Sihketus/ zik\ntas irr ſtarp man/ un ſtarp tew/\naprohz tikkai tawu Mixxonu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrââms paklaufija\nGewronam/ un eefwehre tam to\nNandu/ ka tas bij runnajs teem\nEtta Behrneem dsirdoht/ tschetr-\nsints Sudraba Sihketus/ kas\nPrezzinecku Starpâ tekk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ktua winnam Gew-\nrona Tihruns par ihpaschu/\neekſch\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
